NikiTreats is a static website built with HTML and CSS.
It represents a fictional food brand showcasing a menu, an about section, and a clean design suitable for small restaurants, food bloggers, or culinary portfolios.
This project was created as a beginner-friendly web development project to practice structuring websites, applying CSS for design, and deploying projects to GitHub Pages.

