ğŸ’» How to Use / Run Locally
If you want to run this project on your local computer:

Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/zodenikita/NikiTreats.git

Navigate to the folder
cd NikiTreats

Open index.html in your browser
Just double-click index.html or right-click â†’ "Open with Browser".

ğŸŒ How to Deploy on GitHub Pages
To make this website live:
Push all files to your GitHub repository.

git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit - NikiTreats Website"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/zodenikita/NikiTreats.git
git push -u origin main

Go to your repository on GitHub.
Click on Settings â†’ Pages.
Under Source, select:
Branch: main
Folder: /root
Click Save.

Your website will be live at:
https://zodenikita.github.io/NikiTreats/

